Final result is shown below. Code with syntax highlighting is much more readable for all of us.
```html
@page "/counter"
<h1>Counter</h1>
<p>Current count: @currentCount</p>
<button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="@IncrementCount">Click me</button>
```
```c#
